headline: Chick-fil-A keeps quietly raising prices
summary: Many Americans remember when fast-food chains offered $1 burgers and 50-cent drinks; however, those days are long gone. Today, grabbing a quick meal can feel more like a splurge, with customers often shocked by the high total on their receipts. Fast-food was once the most affordable type of meal ...
